I"_<h1 id="mushroom-stew">Mushroom stew</h1>

<p>Letâ€™s see how to cook your chosen dish.</p>

<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<p>Here is what you need to have at home.</p>

<ol>
  <li>600g, mushrooms, chopped;</li>
  <li>1, onions, finely chopped;</li>
  <li>1 tbsp, lard (alternatively olive oil);</li>
  <li>Seasoning: paprika, black pepper, salt, vegeta mix, garlic;</li>
  <li>150ml, sour cream;</li>
  <li>250g, pasta, small shells.</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Time: Takes as long as it takes.<br />
Serves: Make sure to share, and buy for your pals.</p>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Start playing music in the background.</li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>Add the lard to a sauce pan, and fry the onions.</li>
  <li>Add paprika to the onions, then add the chopped mushrooms.</li>
  <li>Stir until it goes soft, then add vegeta mix and seasoning. Meantime, boil pasta.</li>
  <li>Add little water if necessary, then the sour cream. Grate garlic onto the stew to finish it off.</li>
  <li>Serve on pasta and enjoy.</li>
</ol>

